<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #11998e 0%, #38ef7d 100%);
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 10px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #11998e 0%, #38ef7d 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 40px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 32px;
      }
      .header p {
        margin: 10px 0 0 0;
        font-size: 16px;
        opacity: 0.9;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 40px;
      }
      .greeting {
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .success-box {
        background: #e8f5e9;
        border-left: 4px solid #38ef7d;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 25px 0;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .success-box h3 {
        color: #11998e;
        margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #11998e 0%, #38ef7d 100%);
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 15px 40px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .features {
        background: #f5f5f5;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .features ul {
        margin: 10px 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      .features li {
        margin: 8px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        background: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
        border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>🎉 Congratulations!</h1>
        <p>Your Account is Now Active</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="greeting">
          Hi <strong><%= @user.full_name %></strong>,
        </div>

        <div class="success-box">
          <h3>✓ Account Approved</h3>
          <p>
            Great news! Your Preview Tax expert profile has been <strong>approved by our admin team</strong> at <%= @approved_at %>. 
            Your account is now fully active and ready to use.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p>
          You can now:
        </p>

        <div class="features">
          <ul>
            <li>💰 Add balance in your wallet</li>
            <li>💰 Monitor your transactions and earnings</li>
            <li>📊 Track your insights in real-time</li>
            <li>🎯 Reach thousands of customers</li>
            <li>📱 Manage call and video meetings</li>
            <li>💬 Communicate with customers</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p>
          <a href="<%= ENV['LOGIN_URL'] || 'http://localhost:3001/auth/login' %>" class="button">
            Access Your Account →
          </a>
        </p>

        <p style="background: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;">
          <strong>📧 Tip:</strong> Keep an eye on your inbox for important notifications and updates about 
          your account.
        </p>

        <p>
          If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is here to help. 
          Contact us at <strong>support@previewtax.com</strong>
        </p>

        <p>
          Welcome aboard!<br><strong>Preview Tax Team</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
        <p>© 2026 Preview Tax. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
